          "title": "BETWEEN",
          "summary": "Bill Gates talked with Jessie Woolley-Wilson, a leader in the field of education technology, during this year's ASU+GSV Summit in San Diego. During the talk, they discussed the state of education technology, what the Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation is doing, and the impact AI will have in the months and years ahead. This article contains a transcript of the conversation. A video of the talk is also available.",
